t_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-button-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm\" href=\"https://wa.me/6293089724?text=Tenho%20interesse%20em%20receber%20um%20orcamento\" id=\"facaumorcamento\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">faça um orçamento</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4f27a9e e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"4f27a9e\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b5f7379 e-con-full elementor-hidden-mobile e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"b5f7379\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ba413a8 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"ba413a8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"759\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://aideal.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/2151020055.webp\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-1444\" alt=\"A ideal Soluções Anticorrosivas, especialistas em pintura industrial e revestimentos anticorrosivos de alto desempenho.\" srcset=\"https://aideal.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/2151020055.webp 759w, https://aideal.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/2151020055-228x300.webp 228w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 759px) 100vw, 759px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-333c747 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"333c747\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-372ab17 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"372ab17\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Principais <font color=\"#0B80DF\">Vantagens.</font></h2>\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ff5c338 elementor-icon-list--layout-inline elementor-list-item-link-full_width elementor-widget elementor-widget-icon-list\" data-id=\"ff5c338\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"icon-list.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul class=\"elementor-icon-list-items elementor-inline-items\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"elementor-icon-list-item elementor-inline-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-text\">✅ Baixo Custo</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"elementor-icon-list-item elementor-inline-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-text\">✅ Ambiente limpo</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li class=\"elementor-icon-list-item elementor-inline-item\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-icon-list-text\">✅ Resistência química</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e802c31 elementor-widget__width-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e802c31\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-start=\"242\" data-end=\"333\"><strong>Piso Industrial em Epoxi: Revestimento Monolítico de Alta Resistência para Pisos Industriais.</strong></p><p data-start=\"383\" data-end=\"818\"><strong data-start=\"385\" data-end=\"415\">O Piso industrial epóxi</strong> é uma solução de <strong data-start=\"433\" data-end=\"491\">revestimento de alto desempenho para pisos industriais</strong>, formulada exclusivamente com <strong data-start=\"522\" data-end=\"550\">resinas epoxídicas puras</strong>, sem diluição em água ou solventes. Essa composição garante <strong data-start=\"611\" data-end=\"662\">máxima resistência mecânica, química e abrasiva</strong>, além de uma superfície totalmente <strong data-start=\"698\" data-end=\"737\">impermeável, lisa ou antiderrapante</strong>, ideal para ambientes que exigem <strong data-start=\"771\" data-end=\"817\">durabilidade, segurança e higiene rigorosa</strong>.</p><p data-start=\"820\" data-end=\"1116\">Diferente das tintas epóxi convencionais com base solvente ou base água, a formulação 100% sólidos proporciona uma <strong data-start=\"935\" data-end=\"982\">cobertura mais espessa, uniforme e contínua</strong>, formando um <strong data-start=\"996\" data-end=\"1018\">sistema monolítico</strong> (sem emendas ou juntas), o que impede a proliferação de microrganismos e facilita a higienização.</p><p data-start=\"1118\" data-end=\"1407\">Esse tipo de pintura é amplamente utilizado em <strong data-start=\"1165\" data-end=\"1318\">indústrias alimentícias, farmacêuticas, hospitais, centros logísticos, estacionamentos, laboratórios, cozinhas industriais e áreas de tráfego intenso</strong>, onde o desempenho do piso impacta diretamente na produtividade e segurança do ambiente.</p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-716f90c e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"716f90c\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-885d94a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"885d94a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h5>Vantagens da pintura epóxi 100% sólidos:</h5><ul data-start=\"1454\" data-end=\"1785\"><li data-start=\"1454\" data-end=\"1495\"><p data-start=\"1456\" data-end=\"1495\"><strong data-start=\"1456\" data-end=\"1495\">Alta resistência mecânica e química</strong></p></li><li data-start=\"1496\" data-end=\"1549\"><p data-start=\"1498\" data-end=\"1549\"><strong data-start=\"1498\" data-end=\"1549\">Revestimento monolítico, sem juntas ou fissuras</strong></p></li><li data-start=\"1550\" data-end=\"1597\"><p data-start=\"1552\" data-end=\"1597\"><strong data-start=\"1552\" data-end=\"1597\">Superfície impermeável e de fácil limpeza</strong></p></li><li data-start=\"1598\" data-end=\"1650\"><p data-start=\"1600\" data-end=\"1650\"><strong data-start=\"1600\" data-end=\"1650\">Ideal para áreas que exigem controle sanitário</strong></p></li><li data-start=\"1651\" data-end=\"1695\"><p data-start=\"1653\" data-end=\"1695\"><strong data-start=\"1653\" data-end=\"1695\">Acabamento brilhante ou antiderrapante</strong></p></li><li data-start=\"1696\" data-end=\"1741\"><p data-start=\"1698\" data-end=\"1741\"><strong data-start=\"1698\" data-end=\"1741\">Longa durabilidade com baixa manutenção</strong></p></li><li data-start=\"1742\" data-end=\"1785\"><p data-start=\"1744\" data-end=\"1785\"><strong data-start=\"1744\" data-end=\"1785\">Rápida liberação para uso após a cura</strong></p></li></ul><p data-start=\"1787\" data-end=\"1996\">A <strong data-start=\"1789\" data-end=\"1809\">Ideal Engenharia</strong> executa projetos personalizados com <strong data-start=\"1846\" data-end=\"1883\">pintura epóxi de alta performance</strong>, com equipe especializada e equipamentos modernos, garantindo um acabamento técnico de qualidade e durabilidade.</p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-19d2f73 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"19d2f73\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-147c8a1 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"147c8a1\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-05b2743 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"05b2743\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Obras <font color=\"#0B80DF\">Realizadas.</font></h2>\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5144de8 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"5144de8\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-03772bd gallery-spacing-custom elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget-mobile__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-image-gallery\" data-id=\"03772bd\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image-gallery.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-image-gallery\">\n\t\t\t<div id='gallery-1' class='gallery galleryid-932 gallery-columns-5 gallery-size-medium'><figure class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<div class='gallery-icon landscape'>\n\t\t\t\t<a data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"yes\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"03772bd\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\"A ideal Soluções Anticorrosivas, especialistas em pintura industrial e revestimacento